==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|bestialit|y}}

# {{archaic}} A status of lower [[animal]].
# {{archaic}} An animal-like [[instinct]] or [[behaviour]].
# {{archaic}} A [[mark]], trait, or [[emblem]] of a [[beast]].  "What's your bestiality?  (What's your mark?)"
# Sexual activity between a person and an animal.
# {{dated}} [[Bestial|bestial]] in [[nature]], savagery, [[inhumanity]], like (or akin to) an animal: "Man's bestiality to man"
# {{dated}} Any abstract entity similar to a [[beast]].

